label: dataPrincipal
comment: Detailed information of the source of the data corresponding to this observation.

label: dataProvider
comment: Detailed information of the AIP (Agricultural Information Provider) who aggregates the data from the data principal corresponding to this observation.

label: fileFormat
comment: Format of the file corresponding to this observation.

label: validFrom
comment: The instance from which an official report/document or consent or service corresponding to this observation is valid.

label: validTill
comment: The specific period of time during which a document, authorization, offer or permission remains legally or effectively acceptable/applicable.

label: purposeCode
comment: The unique code representing the consent artifact corresponding to this observation.

label: purposeDescription
comment: Descibes the purpose(s) of the entity or service corresponding this observation.

label: frequency
comment: Represents the frequency of fetching data as allowed by the consent corresponding to this observation. It can have values like 'one-time', 'recurring' or ''three-months"

label: dataConsumerName
comment: The name of the consumer who has been granted access to the data corresponding to this observation.

label: consentArtifactID
comment: The unique identifier assigned by the consent manager to the consent artifact.

label: fileSize
comment: The size of the media file corresponding to this observation
